<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
    <!-- $title = About -->
    <!-- @include assets/meta-head.kit -->
</head>
<body>


<!-- @include assets/header.kit -->


<!-- ========= Hero Section ========= -->
<section class="hero-section after-header" style="height: 500px;" data-disable-resize>
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="background image" style="background-image: url('images/big-backgrounds/table.jpg');" data-parallax="-0.5"></div>

    <!-- Section content -->
    <div class="content remove-padding"><div class="content-inner">
        <h1 class="bold">About us</h1>
    </div></div>
</section>


<!-- ========= Overview section ========= -->
<section class="container big-padding">

    <!-- switcher -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <ul class="tab-toggles">
                <li class="active">
                    <a href="#tab-overview" data-toggle="slick-tab">
                        Overview <i class="entypo right-open-mini"></i>
                    </a>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <a href="#tab-introduction" data-toggle="slick-tab">
                        Introduction <i class="entypo right-open-mini"></i>
                    </a>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <a href="#tab-how-we-grow" data-toggle="slick-tab">
                        How we grow <i class="entypo right-open-mini"></i>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- containers -->
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-1" data-slick-tabs>

            <!-- first tab -->
            <div class="row" id="tab-overview">
                <div class="col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Laoreet quisquam primis totam venenatis cumque, doloribus proident, magnis? Repudiandae praesent habitasse, volutpat mollis velit nesciunt, distinctio reprehenderit class leo enim, exercitation nunc netus morbi aliquip</p></div>

                <div class="col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Ut enim ad minim sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor magna incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea magna consequat.</p></div>
            </div>

            <!-- second tab -->
            <div class="row" id="tab-introduction">
                <!-- image must be 650x430 -->
                <div class="col-md-6"><p class="nolast"><img class="img-responsive" src="images/team/photo4.jpg" alt=""/></p></div>

                <div class="col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Consectetur provident soluta quos, modi magni, aptent irure iure sapien sunt nulla, minim qui? Dolorum explicabo velit fermentum, nostra! Dolores, minima placerat molestiae earum! Nunc deserunt optio! Facilisis primis! Doloremque.</p></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Last tab -->
            <div class="row" id="tab-how-we-grow">
                <div class="col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Rhoncus molestie corrupti molestias? Lorem, arcu aenean possimus, nostra fusce libero quasi. Occaecat corrupti, dolorum. Molestias natus fuga iusto temporibus phasellus condimentum dolorem! Natus sapien.</p></div>

                <div class="col-md-6"><p class="nolast">Iaculis itaque pharetra ipsa illo, repellendus conubia modi per, id expedita? Nemo, cras, venenatis? Maiores eu, vestibulum debitis, nobis officia vel dui elit at deleniti.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="secondary-bg numbers row" data-countup>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
            <div class="number" data-value="9501"></div>
            <div class="text">page views</div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
            <div class="number" data-value="17"></div>
            <div class="text">creative folks</div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
            <div class="number" data-value="103"></div>
            <div class="text">finished projects</div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
            <div class="number" data-value="87"></div>
            <div class="text">donuts</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- ========= Our team section ========= -->
<section class="container-wrap secondary-bg">
    <div class="container big-padding">

        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Meet our team</h2>
            <p class="font-italic">Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Images -->
        <ul class="people-list big-margin block-grid-xs-2 block-grid-sm-4 nogutter">
            <li>
                <img src="images/team/1.jpg" alt="" class="image" />
                <div class="overlay">
                    <h3 class="name">John Doe <small>CEO</small></h3>

                    <ul class="contacts">
                        <li><a href="#">LinkedIn</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Mail</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li>
                <img src="images/team/2.jpg" alt="" class="image" />
                <div class="overlay">
                    <h3 class="name">Mary James <small>designer</small></h3>

                    <ul class="contacts">
                        <li><a href="#">Dribbble</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Mail</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li>
                <img src="images/team/3.jpg" alt="" class="image" />
                <div class="overlay">
                    <h3 class="name">Kiril Ivanov <small>developer</small></h3>

                    <ul class="contacts">
                        <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Mail</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li>
                <img src="images/team/4.jpg" alt="" class="image" />
                <div class="overlay">
                    <h3 class="name">Janny Doe <small>marketer</small></h3>

                    <ul class="contacts">
                        <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>

    </div>
</section>

